{"tid":1509054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15英美議員關注警暴及元朗恐襲 承諾促外交經濟制裁","createTime":"2019-08-26T16:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:10:14.000Z","uid":154277,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"84bbc98bd0377b397bde73b17549e7a0349aa064","tid":1509054,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"反送中運動越演越烈，不少市民在網上聯署、參與眾籌在全球登報，希望進一步引起各國關注。近月亦有人自發向800多名英國國會議員及美國參眾兩院議員發信，已獲其中15人回覆。所有回信的議員均認為香港的人權狀況令人擔憂，部份批評香港政府以過份武力進行鎮壓，又十分關注7.21元朗襲擊事件，指有蒙面幫派襲擊和平示威者，令人無法接受。另外也有議員批評中國政府的行為「展示了中國政權的本質」，承諾將促使英、美政府採取外交及經濟手段進行制裁。<br />\n<br />\nSource 蘋果自己畀錢睇<br />\n<br />\n721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629f18a36ef1ed34b79de796df4d572d97837d66","tid":1509054,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQriUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=ae132586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQriUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=c713702a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQriUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=30139def\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"e64227a6fb47de3057b4b9c1c037c66f06efe504","tid":1509054,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201